data.description: Like-new and impeccably maintained, this 4-bed, 3-bath home offers the perfect space for all your needs. With a spacious master bedroom, guest suite, and an open floor plan with high ceilings, this home feels fresh and inviting. The functional kitchen features quartz countertops and backsplash. Conveniently located near Hwy90 and Hwy 151, shopping, schools, and parks.
